{"tid":179602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新加坡組屋亦有年限　地契完結即收歸國有】","createTime":"2017-03-30T11:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T11:59:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"467cd31360d43e2c5540a490678fc4bdf28dddd4","tid":179602,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"基於《基本法》50年不變的規定，2047大限對地契存續的影響，是2016年立法會競選期間，「熱普城」選舉聯盟的重要議題之一。而屆時樓價想必是大跌，但香港政府並沒有清晰釋除這點疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n而香港的主要競爭城巿新加坡，大部分人居住的組屋（HDB，類似香港的居屋），原來亦有地契的問題，並大部分會在2060年左右到期，當地近期有文章指，即使地契短的組屋亦可轉售到好價錢，因可以換取政府的重整計劃內。但遭到新加坡發展部部長駁斥，指組屋地契完結就會收歸政府所有，而且只有4%組屋能納入重整計劃，呼籲巿民要小心置業。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡媒體在3月24日報道，當地很多新加坡人，特別是執政黨的支持者，都誤以為「仁慈」的政府不會搶走他們的家園。而當地有文章就指，有些屋契較短的舊組屋在二手巿場上，仍可以高價出售，尤其是有購買者抱持舊組屋可納入政府的選擇性整體重建計劃（SERS）內，故不惜以高價購買相關組屋，但事實並非如此。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡的SERS在1995年推出後，只有4%的組屋被納入SERS，當中是具高重新發展潛質的地段，才會被政府接納。而當地的組屋大部分合約在1960年開始<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-30-2017/36930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-30-2017%2F36930&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d98f3e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-30-2017/36930</a><br />\n<br />\n#新加坡 #組屋 #HDB #地契 #SERS #香港 #基本法 #熱普城 #2047大限 #永續基本法<br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=90361c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ec0e8f7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/bpNcBn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbpNcBn&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9733ddea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/bpNcBn</a><br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/IY4fHi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FIY4fHi&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d2dd4bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/IY4fHi</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"66182f6eaa1c3747e8a261df98793ceadee08a4d","tid":179602,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:12:37.000Z","msg":"皮已負"},{"pid":"47f9c57313eefd7cf95f4defef19ce50493afd58","tid":179602,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔好唱衰新加坡ok?"},{"pid":"573381946ebc8aa08969950e328d15d3ed44ec11","tid":179602,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"熱賤兩個狗黨真係好好笑<br />\n<br />\n輸左半年, 到今日都唔明自己錯乜、衰乜？<br />\n<br />\n仲日日大言不慚比人笑？"},{"pid":"e9d8b6f016266770ceed305f25a861ce116cf61e","tid":179602,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好唱衰新加坡ok?</blockquote><br />\n衝入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc642c71f67e12ba29f5f5c7df2c24eebe7cacf","tid":179602,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"做媒體做到劈頭第一句係宣傳自己政黨真係第一次見"},{"pid":"6b07df328e6879dbdb6ef0b5479d8d014506d067","tid":179602,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"呢樣就係我覺得香港應該效法嘅地方，夠期收回再發展，土地得到善用，亦唔會有投機炒賣"},{"pid":"ccb4f954582c24625b525654f8fd431535a64241","tid":179602,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"本土版大紀元<img src=\"/assets/face